				|  your hero, you may choose to change the outcome of your dice roll with the outcome of their original dice roll.
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=sidekick-move5}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Sidekick6')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='sidekick-move6')
				b Journeyman (or Journeywoman)
				| : Take a move that your hero has. Add it to your &quot;Other Moves&quot; section, below.
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=sidekick-move6}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
